      • registerDataset

        public void registerDataset(org.gbif.api.model.common.DOI doi,
                            org.gbif.doi.metadata.datacite.DataCiteMetadata metadata,
                            UUID datasetKey)
                     throws org.gbif.doi.service.InvalidMetadataException
        Description copied from interface: DoiGenerator
        Schedules a DOI metadata update with DataCite and registers the DOI if needed. For subsequent calls with the same DOI only the metadata in DataCite will be updated. If it is called for the very first time the DOI will also be properly registered with DataCite.
        Specified by:
        registerDataset in interface DoiGenerator
        Parameters:
        doi - the GBIF DOI to registerDataset
        metadata - the metadata to post to datacite. Mandatory fields are validated immediately
        datasetKey - the dataset key to derive the target URL from
        Throws:
        org.gbif.doi.service.InvalidMetadataException - in case the metadata is missing mandatory fields or the DOI is not a GBIF one
